text: On one of the Sunday service in JLOJ Revival Hub , I went with my left palm fractured with hospital casting, during the worship, I felt the tangible gentle touch of the God ,sensation was like moving to and fro down my hand , and I just knew God is healing my fractured palm. On my next doctor review appointment , my fractured part was being joined together again, Hallelujah ,all Glory to God , indeed God is our Jehovah Rapha!!
I really feel the extraordinary presence of God in this place.  God bless JLOJ to be even more powerful and a blessing to many people.
Fantastic place to worship and i got lots of annoting and gift from our Lord after i attend JLOJ!Amen.
